<QUOTE PREVIOUSPOST="
mfivespeed wrote:
&gt; i just bought the car ant the guy who owned it be for me had new breaks
&gt; instaled and now the parking break want hold.
">

suggest you remove the drums [if it is drums] and inspect - may not have
been assembled right.  the self-adjusters should take up the slack -
pump the foot brake 20-30 times to do it.  should hear a clicking each
time you release if they're working right.
</POST>
